author: rhuijben
msg: Tweak error messages when trying to resolve move conflicts where the move
information is no longer recorded in wc.db.

author: rhuijben
msg: Fix bad double notifications on replacements of descendants in the move-update
logic that caused an sqlite error.
This problem is/was triggered by the tests added in r1658118.
* subversion/libsvn_wc/wc_db_update_move.c
(tc_editor_add_directory,
tc_editor_add_file): Add old_kind argument. Rename local variable.
Use replace for notification. (update_move_list_add applies the
tree conflicted case when there is one)
(tc_editor_delete): Add new_kind argument and use this to skip
clean delete notifications.
(update_moved_away_node): Update caller.
